  "label": "Ossian Kirth",
  "description": "This individual is an undead human of spare, desiccated build, preserved in the brittle permanence common to the Ossuary Hollow’s long-dead. Pale skin stretches tight across angular bone, with a collapsed nose-bridge and exposed dentition that reduces the face to stark planes and gaps. Gray eyes sit deep in the sockets, glossy and unmoving, beneath gray hair worn in an unkempt fall that clings in thin mats to the scalp. Fine fracture-lines score the jaw and cheekbones, and the hands end in long, darkened nails that read as tools rather than ornaments.",
